bury Town]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} Roland Wycherley<ref>{{cite news | title = Shrewsbury Town restoration needed time, says Wycherley | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17872047 | work = BBC Sport |date= 3 May 2012 | accessdate = 12 February 2013}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\n-\n|[[Southend United F.C.|Southend United]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ron Martin (businessman)|Ron Martin]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Who's Who| url = http://www.southendunited.co.uk/club/whoswho/| work = Southend United F.C |date=22 June 2012 |accessdate = 17 February 2013}}</ref>|\n|\n|[[Property]]\n|-\n|[[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Stewart Donald]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Sunderland sold by Ellis Short as Chris Coleman is sacked|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2018/apr/29/chris-coleman-sackedd-manager-sunderland|accessdate=9 May 2014|work=A.F.C. Sunderland|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180429161912/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2018/apr/29/chris-coleman-sackedd-manager-sunderland|archive-date=29 April 2018|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|{{sort|09|$8.4M}}\n|-\n|[[Tranmere Rovers F.C|Tranmere Rovers]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}}[[Mark Palios]]\n|\n|-\n|[[Wycombe Wanderers F.C.|Wycombe Wanderers]]\n|{{Flagicon|USA}} Rob Couhig (75%)\n\nWycombe Wanderers Supporters Trust (25%)\n| \n|Feliciana EFL Ltd\nSupporters Trust\n|-\n|[[Bolton Wanderers F.C.|Bolton Wanderers]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} Not Ken Anderson <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bwfc.co.uk/club/staff-index/|title=Staff Index|last=|first=|date=|work=Bolton Wanderers F.C.|access-date=|via=}}</ref>\n|$17M<ref>{{cite news|url=https://networthpost.org/net-worth/ken-anderson-net-worth-15/ |title=Ken Anderson Net Worth |website=networthpost.org |access-date=2019-02-21}}</ref>\n|\n|}\n\n==League Two==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Club\n!Owner(s)\n!Estimated<br>combined<br>net worth\n!Source of wealth\n|-\n|[[Bradford City F.C.|Bradford City]]\n|{{Flagicon|Germany}} Stefan Rupp (77,5%)\n\n{{Flagicon