itally Reworked)''<ref>[https://www.deezer.com/en/album/444853 ''Mystery Train (Live but Digitally Reworked)'']</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n|\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''Best of Hank Wilson''<ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/best-of-hank-wilson-mw0000819188 allmusic,  ''Best of Hank Wilson'']</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n|\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''The Best of Leon Russell''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.last.fm/music/Leon+Russell/The+Best+of+Leon+Russell|title=The Best of Leon Russell \u2014 Leon Russell|website=Last.fm|accessdate=April 30, 2019}}</ref><ref name=SD-2011>{{cite web | url=https://theseconddisc.com/2011/04/review-leon-russell-the-best-of-leon-russell/ | title=Review: Leon Russell, The Best of Leon Russell | publisher=The Second Disc | date=April 7, 2011 | accessdate=March 20, 2017}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''Snapshot''<ref>[https://www.allmusic.com/album/snapshot-mw0002597667 allmusic,  ''Snapshot'']</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''The Montreux Session''<ref>[https://www.discogs.com/Leon-Russell-The-Montreux-Session/release/6713359 discogs.com ''The Montreux Session'']</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n|\n|-\n| colspan=\"11\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:80%;\"| \"\u2014\" denotes releases that did not chart.\n|}\n\n===Singles===\n<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.musicvf.com/songs.php?page=artist&artist=Leon+Russell&tab=songaswriterchartstab|title=Leon Russell \u2022 Top Songs as Writer \u2022 Music VF, US & UK hits charts|website=Musicvf.com|accessdate=April 30, 2019}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Single\n! colspan=\"6\"| Chart positions\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! style=\"width:3.5em;font-size:75%;\"| [[Billboard Hot 100|U.S.]]<br /><ref name=\"whitburn2010\">{{cite book | author=Joel Whitburn | title=Top Pop Singles 1955\u20132010 | publisher=Record Research, Inc. | page=776 | year=2011 |